<Layout title="Chain Settlements in Brisbane: When Your Buyer Is Selling Another Property on the Same Day | Daniel Gierach Property" description="Your buyer needs the proceeds of their own sale to fund yours. Here is how chain settlements actually work in Brisbane, where they break, and how to protect your position as a seller." schema={faqSchema}>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
